    can sell families and make screenshots of them to share to aysia and everyone
    else
    <h1>Extreme</h1>
    can REALLY make families, which can make them everywhere and sell them. if the
    extreme turkey made everyone, nobody's in the world!
    <h1>X</h1>
    is the main force of the family team, which can be very good at families. this
    means you can make little girls. these are secret. the main secret one is Kate
    <h2>What turkey are you?</h2>
    <h3>a normal family</h3>
    there are usually 6 people in the families. sometimes, there is actually 5. secret
    girls are hidden in my town world

    <h1>who do you want to know about?</h1>
    <select name="" id="">
      <option value="">None</option>
      <option value="">Named</option>
      <option value="">All families</option>
      <option value="">Everyone</option>
      <option value="">Everyone in the world</option>
    </select>
    <h2>Ranking</h2>
    1. ladi franka
    <br />
    2. fahon migily
    <br />
    3. oscar jones
    <br />
    4. snally ree
    <br />
    5. poetry magnasa
    <details>
      <summary>More</summary>
      <div>
        6. kate jones
        <br />
        7. billy rock
        <br />
        8. james kempton
        <br />
        9. allison cook
        <br />
        10. nora nere
      </div>
    </details>
    <h1>That's everyone</h1>
    <select name="" id="">
      <option value="">Awful</option>
      <option value="">Bad</option>
      <option value="">Not sure</option>
      <option selected value="">Good</option>
      <option value="">Great</option>
      <option value="">SUPER!</option>
    </select>
    <select name="" id="">
