    make sure your options are at "good" "job"
    <br />
    like this:
    <h1>Step 4</h1>
    open the "Z" summary
    <h1>Step 5</h1>
    press the little buttons like:
    <br />
    <button></button>
    <h1>Step 6</h1>
    measure all the things to unlock this
    <h1>Step 7</h1>
    read all the turkey types
    <h1>Step 8</h1>
